---
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Google AI Optimisation UK - Rank4AI | AI Overviews & Gemini" description="Google AI optimisation for UK businesses. Get cited in Google AI Overviews and Gemini. Build presence across Google's 20+ platforms.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Google Ai Optimisation' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Google AI Optimisation</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Google AI Optimisation UK</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility signals" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Google AI Overviews appear at the top of search results, replacing traditional links with AI-generated answers. Gemini is Google's AI assistant. Google AI Mode is the new dedicated AI search tab. All three pull from different combinations of signals - but all favour businesses with strong presence across Google's own infrastructure.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI builds your presence across 20+ Google-owned platforms. When content is published there, it does not need to be discovered. It is already inside the system Google AI Overviews and Gemini draw from.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">For the full guides, see <a href="/learn/guides/google-ai-overview-optimisation/" class="link">Google AI Overview Optimisation</a> and <a href="/learn/guides/google-ai-mode/" class="link">Google AI Mode Optimisation</a>.</p>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/complete-guide-ai-search/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Complete AI Search Guide</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
